  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Puzzles are waiting for you!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827910/extras/e8d1975626ec11377b1bc2d9afe9b8e5.avif?t=1723772166\" width=559 height=220 /></span><br>An amazing world of puzzles awaits you in <strong>TileTurn! </strong>Relax while playing through beautiful swap puzzles, 60 levels of art puzzles made in different styles will help you with this, and wonderful relaxing music will also help them!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features of the game:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>60 levels!<br></li><li>Fascinating gameplay!<br></li><li>Amazing visual!<br></li><li>Soothing music!<br></li><li>Steam Achievements!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827910/extras/a7ecd9e7e4d2389cb7922e2f5e303966.poster.avif?t=1723772166\" width=460 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827910/extras/a7ecd9e7e4d2389cb7922e2f5e303966.webm?t=1723772166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827910/extras/a7ecd9e7e4d2389cb7922e2f5e303966.mp4?t=1723772166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
